name: BMI Brow Mastery International Aesthetics n Cosmetology Academy

reviews.text: I recommend the training course from Doctor Jenny. Its a one on one training and she is very thorough on her teaching and sharing her knowledge. She made me focused and have a fun learning as well. She made me improve the skills that i am lacking and it made me confident to handle clients as well. It was a memorable learning and fun experience. Thank you Doc Jenny.

Superb glad to meet with Jenny personally and having her for conducting 1 to 1 sessions with me.

Jenny is a nice, friendly, capable, patient, knowledgeable, experience and professional teacher / coach.

I had enrolled 3-days course on eyelash extensions course with zero knowledge and experience, I had learnt a new skills and tactics through her guidance.

During the course day, she made me feel ultimate relax and always boost my confidence to strive better by sharing her experiences.

Lastly, I strongly recommend YOU (reading this review) to choose Jenny Wong as your coach to pick up the skills set and she will provides guidances on the career path, equip you with proper knowledge so to avoid unnecessary journey by getting started in the industry!

I attened the 2 days Microblading course in Brows Mastery. The class was amazing and definitely worth it. The training provided us a lot of knowledge with both hands on and theory. Miss Jenny Wong is very professional and knowledgeable. She excels in professional application skills and also provides support and career advancement to the student. Everything is so thorough and very detailed, she would make sure we were doing as instructed in the end I feel like I definitely chose the best school would 100% recommend!

Two thumbs up! Jenny is great as a coach and teacher as she's not only detailed but also very patient. Do consider BrowMastery Academy if you are planning to learn a good set of skills from Jenny and team.
